{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"typedef","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The handler receives two parameters:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it failed"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"error"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": An error object if registration failed, or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it succeeded"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"]}],"metadata":{"title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"fragments":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}],"roleHeading":"Type Alias","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"typealias"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshRegistrationHandler":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler","title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshErrorHandler":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshErrorHandler"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when an operation fails.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosherrorhandler","title":"PushwooshErrorHandler","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshFramework","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/title","value":"PushwooshErrorHandler","op":"replace"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshErrorHandler"}],"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/fragments","op":"replace"}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}